news.headline: Starbucks Elects Two Board Members Including Former Yahoo CEO Marissa Mayer
news.summary: Marissa Mayer is now chief executive of Sunshine AI, a technology startup she founded that automates everyday tasks. The coffee chain also added Dambisa Moyo to the board.
